reviewText: You cannot find these classic Hanna-Barbera cartoons anywhere on TV or You Tube! I was telling my grandchildren about them, looked on the internet. I am so glad my VCR still works. Seeing my grandkids giggle at the same thing I did warms my heart. Thanks
This VHS tape is in great condition and played perfectly .A little wear on the case. Very satisfied and my son loves it.
my sister asked me to order this for my nephew and he's loved it since he got it...it was a christmas gift
